To Release
----------

(Notes.)

Commit all changes.

Run tests:
PERL5LIB=. perl XML/t/01_main.t

Bump version in:
	Writer.pm
	Makefile.PL
	META.yml

Update changelog.

svn commit XML

svn mkdir tags/release-A_BCD
svn cp trunk/XML tags/release-A_BCD/

Locally,

svn export tags/release-A_BCD /tmp/xml-writer-release

perl Makefile.PL
make dist

Upload to Berlios, CPAN.

Update web page:
./gen-index.pl >generated-index.html && scp generated-index.html shell.berlios.de:/home/groups/xml-writer-perl/htdocs/index.html
